text: Þis is rimtunes land boc ðe Æþelstan cing gebocode Æþerede his þegne on ece yrfæ.
Ðis syndon þes landesgemære æt Rimtune.
Ærest of hig broce suþ andlang dic on ðone herpað.
West andlang herpaðes on wendan mære on morþ dic.
Þonon norð &lang herpaðes on wiðig leas wyrttruman.
Þonne ealling be wyrttruman oþ aclea eastewearðne & nordþeweardne.
Þanon on hig broc east &lang broces on þes hiwisces dic.
Nord &lang dices on þæt strod east &lang strodes.
Of þam strode on wederangrafe scagan.
Andlang beas broces þonne suþ be wyrttruman eft on hig broc.
